description.plain:
This song is featured only on the ‘Deluxe Edition’ of Reflektor, as the penultimate track;

Much like other, similarly themed, songs on the album, the song addresses life after death, telling the story of someone who wants to ‘get right’ before they die (i.e. rid of their sins so they can go to heaven).

Much of the album addresses myth, particularly myth and speculation around the ‘afterlife’. This track is a short continuation of the ongoing theme itself.

